OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1774887078
OL,3,CCity centre footbridge closes
OL,4,Cfollowing discovery of 'structural
OL,5,Cdefect'
OL,7,FA major footbridge in Carlisle city
OL,8,Fcentre has closed following the
OL,9,Fdiscovery of a crack in a steel
OL,10,Fcomponent.
OL,12,FCumberland Council engineers closed
OL,13,Fthe Irish Gate crossing "as a
OL,14,Fprecaution" after routine inspection
OL,15,Fwork found the structural issue in a
OL,16,Fpart supporting the bridge deck.
OL,18,FThe council says that while pedestrian
OL,19,Faccess to the bridge is closed, there
OL,20,Fis no risk to users below and Castle
OL,21,FWay remains fully open.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/3
