CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1774887078
OL,3,CCity centre footbridge closes
OL,4,Cfollowing discovery of 'structural
OL,5,Cdefect'
OL,7,FEngineers have now been tasked with
OL,8,Fcarrying out detailed investigations
OL,9,Fto determine the extent of the problem
OL,10,Fand "determine the most appropriate
OL,11,Fnext steps".
OL,13,FThe council said: "Public safety
OL,14,Fremains the council's priority
OL,15,Fthroughout."
OL,17,FNo re-opening date or timescale has
OL,18,Fbeen given.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/3
