OL,3,CCity centre footbridge closes
OL,4,Cfollowing discovery of 'structural
OL,5,Cdefect'
OL,7,FCumberland Council promises that
OL,8,Ffurther updates will be shared as more
OL,9,Finformation becomes available, and it
OL,10,Fsaid it "appreciates the public's
OL,11,Fpatience".
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
